com.emitrom.flash4j.tween.client.core

Class TweenCore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emitrom.flash4j.core.client.ProxyObject
      • com.emitrom.flash4j.tween.client.core.TweenCore
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimpleTimeLine, TweenLite

    public class TweenCore
extends ProxyObject
    TweenCore is the base class for all TweenLite, TweenMax, TimelineLite, and TimelineMax classes and provides core functionality and properties. There is no reason to use this class directly.
